 He sent out another  message to all the decepticon wavelengths he felt. "I am 
Carnatton, I have fallen into something, " he looked down at his black 
suit, "if you wish ultimate victory, a true decepticon victory we must work 
togeather meet me here." He could feel one strong telepathic precense. He 
wondered if this bots abilites matched what the suit gave him. He look out 
pulling the images of all the bases with his mind towards him his mind's eye 
watching the happenings. Hydra's was on his way to Optimus. He then tracked 
the large psychic presence and saw a group of bots he pulled back not wanting 
to waste his energy.
